---
title: Hearty Pork Meatballs and Mushroom Stew with Parmesan Mash
description: Meatballs and mushroom stew is the food equivalent of a well-worn, fuzzy sweater: familiar and warm. We've packed this recipe with classic winter veggies and savoury flavours for a timeless dish, that never goes out of fashion.
